profile:
Doorcraft Manufacturing Ltd. is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving the Fredericton area. We would love for you to visit our showroom at 1921 Hanwell Road. There, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program.  

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door. We are a member of the (CDI).  

We have five employees ready to give you the fastest service in the industry. Our showroom is located at 22 Durelle Street, Unit 3 in Fredericton and is open Monday to Friday from 8:00 AM to 5:00 PM and Saturday by appointment. 

I invite you to come and visit us, and on behalf of our entire team, I thank you for considering our company. 

Joey Hebert
Owner
Doorcraft Manufacturing Ltd.
hours: Monday to Friday from 8 AM to 5 PM, Evenings and Saturdays by appointment.
